config.DefaultGrassWeight.name: Default Grass Weight
config.DefaultGrassWeight.desc: The weight value of base game grass, affects how frequently they appear. Default 0 (never).
config.MoreGrassShimWeight.name: More Grass Shim Weight
config.MoreGrassShimWeight.desc: The weight value of grass loaded from More Grass, affects how frequently they appear. Default 3.
